This paper deals with the performance gains of optimal antenna deployment for massive MIMO systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), system and control theory (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
